                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                        Why is recovery as important as training?
                        <span class="faq-icon"></span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Muscles repair and strengthen during rest. Without sufficient recovery, you risk overtraining and injuries. AIVancePro analyzes your load and alerts you if your volume is too high.</div></div>
